VITAMIN & MINERALS: CALCIUM CARBONATE, VITAMIN C (SODIUM ASCORBATE), NIACINAMIDE, VITAMIN A (PALMITATE), ZINC (ZINC OXIDE), REDUCED IRON, VITAMIN B6 (PYRIDOXINE HYDROCHLORIDE), VITAMIN B2 (RIBOFLAVIN), VITAMIN D (CHOLECALCIFEROL), VITAMIN B1 (THIAMINE HYDROCHLORIDE), FOLIC ACID, VITAMIN B12 (CYANOCOBALAMIN).
